column6: - The first appearance of the Avengers of the Supernatural! - When the producers of the Mojoverse can't make a hit series they call on Mojo to gather an all-new, all-creepy Avengers! - Can the Uncanny Avengers survive the wrath of an unleashed Spirit of Vengeance?
column8: | penciller (cover):Art Adams | writer:Rick Remender | artist:Paul Renaud
